[normal]ke more of the UK’s reputation for high quality research and our attractiveness as a destination for foreign direct investment. 
[normal]The UK can
[normal] build on this to work with others in addressing challenges that nation states cannot tackle alone, to share costs and
[normal] risks, accelerate technology development and 
[normal]disseminate
[normal] lessons learned.
[normal]47.
