[normal]The UK also works in partnership with other countries, with RCUK offices in China, India and USA. Over the last few years RCUK has funded activities in key technologies with China i
[normal]n renewable energy generation technologies, CCS, fuel cells
[normal], energy storage
[normal] and smart grids worth 
[normal]£30m
