[normal] stimulat
[normal]es
[normal] and 
[normal]support
[normal]s
[normal] 
[normal]business-led innovation with an investment of £1bn over the spending review period, which is doubled by partn
[normal]er and business contributions.  Priority theme areas, with a low carbon focus, are energy, transport and the built environment.
